
extends layout

block content
  div.container
    h1 #{mainHeader}
      blockquote
        p User stories:
          ul
            li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
            br
            li If I pass an invalid URL that doesn't follow the valid http://www.example.com format, the JSON response will contain an error instead.
            br
            li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.
                    
    h3 Example creation usage:
    p
      code https://erichoog-surl.herokuapp.com/new/https://www.google.com
    p
      code https://erichoog-surl.herokuapp.com/new/http://www.freecodecamp.com/news
      
    h3 Example creation output:
    p
      code { "original_url": "http://www.freecodecamp.com/news", "short_url": "https://erichoog-surl.herokuapp.com/4" }
      
    h3 Usage:
    p
      code https://erichoog-surl.herokuapp.com/4
      
    h3 Will redirect to:
    p
      code http://www.freecodecamp.com/news